t: "Si tawaama wonnde …ďe hanndi e bakkaatu, ko wo…ó…ďe …ói…óo darotoo darnde ma…ď…ďe nden, hara ko jeyaa…ďe e hanndu…ďe e hettugol , …ďe woondira Alla : \"Pellet, ko seedee amen on …ďuri jojjude seedee ma…ď…ďe on ; men jaggitaali. Menen ontuma [si men wa…óii …óum], haray men jeyaama e too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"